    "description": "Hide &amp; Seek is a fast pace, multiplayer game between police vs thieves! Plan your next heist and steal treasures from the map. Choose your role! You play as a guard or a thief. <br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>As the guard, your main objective is to find and take down all the thieves before they steal all the treasures.<br></li><li> Like a thief, you have to steal all the treasures at a certain time. Be aware and don't get caught!</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705510/extras/abcfab8542e73189f4aa2c28b377c5ee.poster.avif?t=1644515687\" width=600 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705510/extras/abcfab8542e73189f4aa2c28b377c5ee.webm?t=1644515687\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705510/extras/abcfab8542e73189f4aa2c28b377c5ee.mp4?t=1644515687\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </h2>Play with friends or random players from all over the world! You can play on public servers or host your own.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705510/extras/8143c384d0785838d8f45ac39c2bba1e.poster.avif?t=1644515687\" width=600 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705510/extras/8143c384d0785838d8f45ac39c2bba1e.webm?t=1644515687\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705510/extras/8143c384d0785838d8f45ac39c2bba1e.mp4?t=1644515687\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </h2>Customize your look. Choose from dozens of different skins and play as your favorite character!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705510/extras/bc1c2862f3109d0e70b1ae198fbe8b10.poster.avif?t=1644515687\" width=600 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705510/extras/bc1c2862f3109d0e70b1ae198fbe8b10.webm?t=1644515687\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705510/extras/bc1c2862f3109d0e70b1ae198fbe8b10.mp4?t=1644515687\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </h2>Hide &amp; Seek is an easy play, but hard to master game that encourages strategy and skill! During each round, the locations of the treasure chests and powerful power-ups are randomly selected. Play with teammates to win and do 200 IQ moves to tip the balance of the gameplay!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705510/extras/a9f893ffd86639891da46d7b5a5179ba.poster.avif?t=1644515687\" width=600 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705510/extras/a9f893ffd86639891da46d7b5a5179ba.webm?t=1644515687\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705510/extras/a9f893ffd86639891da46d7b5a5179ba.mp4?t=1644515687\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </h2>Familiar rules of thieves vs cops game in a completely new form! Steal or defend treasures. Play with or against friends!",
